  "title": "The data_sub() function returns null when using extreme base date",
  "description": "## Bug Report\n\nPlease answer these questions before submitting your issue. Thanks!\n\n### 1. Minimal reproduce step (Required)\n\n```sql\nselect date_sub('0000-01-01 00:00:00', interval '-1-0' YEAR_MONTH);\n```\n\n### 2. What did you expect to see? (Required)\n\nmysql8\n\n```sql\n+-------------------------------------------------------------+\n| date_sub('0000-01-01 00:00:00', interval '-1-0' YEAR_MONTH) |\n+-------------------------------------------------------------+\n| 0001-01-01 00:00:00                                         |\n+-------------------------------------------------------------+\n1 row in set (0.00 sec)\n\n```\n\n### 3. What did you see instead (Required)\n\n```sql\n+-------------------------------------------------------------+\n| date_sub('0000-01-01 00:00:00', interval '-1-0' YEAR_MONTH) |\n+-------------------------------------------------------------+\n| NULL                                                        |\n+-------------------------------------------------------------+\n1 row in set, 1 warning (0.00 sec)\n\n```\n\n### 4. What is your TiDB version? (Required)\n\n```sql\n+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n| tidb_version()                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |\n+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n| Release Version: v7.5.1\nEdition: Community\nGit Commit Hash: 7d16